data.actual_result: Image Uploader Bar overlaps unread message bar.
data.expected_result: Both Image Uploader and Unread Message Bars are separate.
data.short_description: Image Uploader Bar overlaps Unread Message Bar.
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to a text channel with many unread messages. - Upload an image to the said channel. - Screenshot as the image is uploading. - View the screenshot and zoom in to see how they overlap.
